CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. It designates the name of the sponsoring entity for the beneficial owner that is one of the following: (a) a sponsored Foreign Financial Institution (FII) without a GIIN number, OR (b) a certified deemed- compliant closely held investment vehicle, or (c) a sponsored direct reporting NFFE, as these entities are defined by IRS forms W-8.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The name of the sponsoring entity for the beneficial owner, these entities are defined by IRS forms W-8.
CustomField.label: Form W8 Sponsor Entity Name
